      <h1 class="text-[12vw] leading-[0.8] font-black font-jakarta text-yokai-white tracking-tighter uppercase text-center [text-shadow:0_4px_24px_rgba(42,30,82,0.8)] mix-blend-overlay opacity-90">
        YOKAI<br/>
        <span class="text-yokai-purple italic font-outfit tracking-[0.2em]">WOTAGEI</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="absolute bottom-16 right-12 text-xs font-inter font-bold tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-yokai-white/80 [text-shadow:0_1px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]">
        Yogyakarta Wotagei Team
